{"id":4240,"date":"2025-06-16T16:49:50","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:49:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4240"},"modified":"2025-07-20T00:05:40","modified_gmt":"2025-07-19T17:05:40","slug":"vi-sao-dung-kem-chong-nang-bi-noi-mun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/vi-sao-dung-kem-chong-nang-bi-noi-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u00ec sao d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201ct\u1ea5m khi\u00ean\u201d c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng gay g\u1eaft v\u00e0 tia UV c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng <\/span><b>d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng g\u00e2y n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u00f9ng da m\u1eb7t \u2013 n\u01a1i nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec sao d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n? Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, th\u00f3i quen ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh da c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. C\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay 6 l\u00fd do ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da \u201cph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng\u201d v\u1edbi kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi-sao-dung-kem-chong-nang-bi-noi-mun\"><\/span><b>V\u00ec sao d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-sai-loai-san-pham-so-voi-loai-da\"><\/span><b>D\u00f9ng sai lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m so v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m theo c\u1ea3m t\u00ednh, ch\u1ea1y theo trend hay nghe theo review t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c b\u00ed b\u00e1ch, sinh m\u1ee5n. Da d\u1ea7u, da kh\u00f4, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m &#8211; m\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang, r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam nang l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chi-so-spf-qua-cao\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF qu\u00e1 cao\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF c\u00e0ng cao th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 SPF v\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft (tr\u00ean 50) th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u00ed t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u1edf da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u00e1nh n\u1eafng, vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng SPF qu\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 khi\u1ebfn da \u201cph\u1ea3n kh\u00e1ng\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4241\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4241\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4241\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-1.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF qu\u00e1 cao\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4241\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF qu\u00e1 cao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sach-da-chua-dung-cach\"><\/span><b>L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac b\u00e1m d\u00ednh cao. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da k\u1ef9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y, c\u00e1c l\u1edbp kem c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u00e2m th\u1ea7m nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <\/span><b>b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb l\u00ean m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoa-qua-nhieu-kem-trong-mot-lan\"><\/span><b>Thoa qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kem trong m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9 b\u00f4i d\u00e0y kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 da s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecbt k\u00edn, khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4ng \u201cth\u1edf\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. Thoa v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ec1u tay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4242\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4242\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4242\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-2.webp\" alt=\"Thoa qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kem trong m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4242\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thoa qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kem trong m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-tay-trang-moi-ngay\"><\/span><b>Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, vi\u1ec7c <\/span>t\u1ea9y trang v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u1eabn l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c. Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 tr\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang k\u1ef9 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u00e0n d\u01b0 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean da, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00ed l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4243\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4243\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4243\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-3.webp\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4243\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ban-tay-ban-%e2%80%93-nguyen-nhan-it-ai-de-y\"><\/span><b>B\u00e0n tay b\u1ea9n &#8211; nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u00edt ai \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f4i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o l\u00ean m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda tay s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd. Tay l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 vi khu\u1ea9n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00ean m\u1eb7t qua thao t\u00e1c thoa kem, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n sinh s\u00f4i, g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-phong-ngua-mun-khi-su-dung-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5n do ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng g\u00e2y ra, h\u00e3y l\u01b0u \u00fd nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4244\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4244\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4244\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-4.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/73-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4244\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m oil-free ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 nh\u00e3n \u201cnon-comedogenic\u201d \u2013 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a Zinc Oxide ho\u1eb7c Titanium Dioxide n\u1ebfu da b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n nh\u01b0: Isopropyl Myristate, Myristyl Myristate, Octyl Stearate\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lu\u00f4n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea9y trang v\u00e0 r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">R\u1eeda tay s\u1ea1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi khu\u1ea9n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi da m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thoa l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kem v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 theo khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb: kho\u1ea3ng 2 \u0111\u1ed1t ng\u00f3n tay cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>V\u00ec sao d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u sai v\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ea1n \u201cbi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh\u201d m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc. H\u00e3y ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7. Khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u00ec sao d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n?  Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n da d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4243,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4240","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4240","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4240"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4240\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4417,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4240\/revisions\/4417"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4243"}],"wp:a